data.description: Here is the home that you have been searching for, almost 1900 sq ft of living space, all on one floor! The home is move-in ready and has a new wood pellet stove to use as a main heat source or as supplemental heat. Large rooms throughout the home. There is a nice large yard and a beautiful stamped concrete patio to relax on. The 36x28 insulated and heated garage is also a great area to relax in or work on some hobbies and projects! The garage does have electric baseboard heaters and a new pellet stove as well! All of this on 1.12 acres.
